Class FileDirectoryMeasurement

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.surveyaction.measurements.FileDirectoryMeasurement
public class FileDirectoryMeasurement extends Object
FileDirectoryMeasurement describes the measurements that are typically captured when a file system is surveyed.
